.TH start-cli-backup-review-decide 1  "decide "
.SH NAME
start\-cli\-backup\-review\-decide \- Resolve automatic backup decisions for a newly installed service
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBstart\-cli backup review decide\fR <\fB\-\-decision\fR> [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPACKAGE_ID\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Resolve automatic backup decisions for a newly installed service
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-decision\fR \fI<DECISIONS>\fR
Decision as JOB_ID=add or JOB_ID=skip; repeat for every affected job
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIPACKAGE_ID\fR>
Package identifier
